{"tid":183052,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養狗巴絲請入","createTime":"2017-04-01T18:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T08:15:18.000Z","uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11675edb117874390e079a4d929f2f816cb3fce3","tid":183052,"uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"有啲關於隻狗散步問題想請教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屋企住村屋，養咗兩隻狗<br />\n第一隻每次出門口散步，只肯行附近兩三間屋嘅範圍，個感覺似巡地盤多過散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我帶佢行多啲都唔肯，會坐喺條路到唔肯郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二隻佢一定要跟住第一隻，如果唔係就連門口都唔肯出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想請問各位巴絲，有咩好建議我應該點做？同埋係咪要考慮搵trainer?麻煩各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed2f13c0b672269dda2ad6b6cbd4df41399e152","tid":183052,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"應該係驚，試吓用食物引佢行前"},{"pid":"e89164879a0b6ecbe42e016eae4bc0e0723b3a8f","tid":183052,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會平時喺屋企跑得多 冇乜興趣出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：住細屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻狗一出街就好興奮"},{"pid":"445c8d59d75a1db44a101cd6a483e5fc494d8dfa","tid":183052,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"幾多歲呀你隻狗狗 養左幾耐？"},{"pid":"876cbd7bb64e839d2e8501bfff698173e77b99b5","tid":183052,"uid":3952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"佢唔想行做咩要逼佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d57dc6400995989b63f61bad4b578ce235497f","tid":183052,"uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多歲呀你隻狗狗 養左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n大嗰隻4歲，細嗰隻一歲<br />\n養咗4,5個月"},{"pid":"03bfccbf6ff0356dce4be587d7c52d392b9b20d3","tid":183052,"uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會平時喺屋企跑得多 冇乜興趣出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：住細屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻狗一出街就好興奮</blockquote><br />\n兩隻都好懶，又怕熱鐘意吹冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地知有得出街會好開心，不過就唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d1bf44d5f3d9e801d436715cadf46ffa771b0e","tid":183052,"uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔想行做咩要逼佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再唔郁就會變肥狗，獸醫都叫要減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5af41da5c165841f73fc0c118f7aafa549b3268","tid":183052,"uid":10701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係驚，試吓用食物引佢行前</blockquote><br />\n有呀，食完就調頭行返入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f00bd10eec8c9a4b8831007f13bfe65c266f654","tid":183052,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"佢地有冇同過其他狗狗玩？"}]}